                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9473" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1429</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">805 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">古艺熠熠：“老石家”百草梨膏糖的活化之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ancient Art Shines: The Way to Revitalize the “LAOSHIJIA BAICAOLIGAOTANG”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈汉辉，梅昊雪，姚馨，高深圳，杨雨婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蚌埠梨膏堂食品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">老字号；老石家百草梨膏糖；品牌活化；营销创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Time-honored Brands, LAOSHIJIA BAICAOLIGAOTANG, Brand Revitalization, Marketing Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">老字号品牌是中国传统文化的瑰宝，沿袭并传承了中华民族的优秀文化传统，是我国重要的文化资产。随着时代的发展，众多老字号品牌日渐衰败甚至消失，但老石家百草梨膏糖却焕发出新的活力。本案例以“老石家”百草梨膏糖陷入品牌老化的困境为背景，以老石家的品牌活化之路为主线，列举了“老石家”在品牌活化方面如何破局所采取的一系列措施，进而探讨了老字号企业如何传承和创新传统文化、工艺元素以满足消费者多样化的需求。面对挑战，“老石家”百草梨膏糖在传承文化的同时，紧跟时代变化，抓住实时热点，善用网络传媒工具，在品牌营销过程中融入时尚而有创意的当地传统文化元素增强品牌感染力，拓宽品牌的使用场景，增强品牌的知名度，加大品牌的影响力，从而实现品牌活化。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Time-honored brands are the treasure of traditional Chinese culture, inheriting and carrying forward the excellent cultural traditions of the Chinese nation, and are important cultural assets in China. With the development of the times, many time-honored brands have gradually declined or even disappeared, but LAOSHIJIA BAICAOLIGAOTANG has emerged with new vitality. This case study is based on the background of LAOSHIJIA BAICAOLIGAOTANG falling into the dilemma of brand aging, and takes the brand activation path of LAOSHIJIA as the main line. It lists a series of measures taken by LAOSHIJIA to break the deadlock in brand activation, and then discusses how time-honored enterprises can inherit and innovate traditional culture and craft elements to meet the diverse needs of consumers. Facing challenges, while inheriting culture, LAOSHIJIA BAICAOLIGAOTANG keeps up with the changes of the times, seizes real-time hot spots, makes good use of online media tools, integrates fashionable and creative local traditional cultural elements into the brand marketing process to enhance brand appeal, broaden the use scenarios of the brand, enhance brand awareness, increase brand influence, and achieve brand activation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌老化；STP理论；4P、4C和4R营销理论；品牌传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
